## Report archive

To build trends, use `/apg-java-release-audit archive` to save reports under `.claude/audit-reports/java-release/YYYY/MM/DD/`, then use `compare` or `trend` to analyze quality changes.

## Stop conditions

If P0 issues are found or evidence is insufficient to judge release risk, do not conclude “release is acceptable”; output blockers or a “needs further verification” list.
